===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''dinosaur''' (''plural:'' '''[[dinosaurs]]''')
# Any of various [[extinct]] [[reptile]]s existing between about 230 million and 65 million years ago.
# (''figurative, colloquial'') A person who is very old or has very old-fashioned views.

